name: 50 Abstract posters/wallpapers
description:
This file is more like a collection. It all started I was practicing and exploring gradient colors in Figma. Now it's an open-source to share my learning and practicing. Give back to what I've learned 😊.


• 🎁 All designs were made with Figma. Feel free to edit and explore. Have fun with it !

• 💡 My inspirations from: Figma community, Pinterest, Instagram, Dribbble, Behance, Youtube...

• ✨ I will keep adding more designs to this file.


Got TONS of inspirations and learned tips & tricks here and there. Hope this file inspires your next design project in some way. ❤️❤️❤️
